<metal:block i18n:domain="schooltool">
  <div class="header" i18n:translate="">
    What is This?
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <p i18n:translate="">
      In addition to entering skill data through SchoolTool's web interface, you
      can also import skill data from a spreadsheet using this template:
      <a i18n:name="link-to-empty-data-file" href="empty_skills_data.xls"
         tal:attributes="href context/++resource++empty_skills_data.xls">empty_skills_data.xls</a>.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
      Data included in the spreadsheet will be added to data in the system;
      importing will not cause data to be removed.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
      You do not have to import all worksheets at the same time.  You can import
      individual worksheets sequentially.
    </p>
  </div>
</metal:block>
